"title": "8754: fear",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8754",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>An attitude of anxiety or distress, caused by concern over a threat to one's future. Scripture provides numerous examples of situations in which fear is experienced. It declares, however, that God alone is to be feared, and moments of human fear can be opportunities for deepening faith in him.</p>\n<h2>Reverent fear of God commended</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:7\">PRO 1:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:13\">DEU 6:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:12-Deut31:13\">DEU 31:12–31:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh4:24\">JOS 4:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh24:14\">JOS 24:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:24\">1SA 12:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps2:11\">PSA 2:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:7-Ps34:9\">PSA 34:7–34:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:33\">PRO 15:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:13\">ECC 12:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:6\">ISA 33:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:7\">REV 14:7</a></p>\n<h2>Fear of natural phenomena</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:5\">PSA 91:5</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah1:4-Jonah1:5\">JON 1:4–1:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:30\">GEN 19:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:22\">JOB 5:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:5\">ECC 12:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa7:25\">ISA 7:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:26\">MAT 8:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:13\">REV 11:13</a></p>\n<h2>Fear of the unnatural</h2>\n<h3>Fear of thoughts and visions</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:5\">DAN 4:5</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:4\">ACT 10:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam3:15\">1SA 3:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job4:13-Job4:15\">JOB 4:13–4:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa21:4\">ISA 21:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan8:17\">DAN 8:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:11-Dan10:12\">DAN 10:11–10:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:20\">MAT 1:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:4\">MAT 28:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:12-Luke1:13\">LUK 1:12–1:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:29-Luke1:30\">LUK 1:29–1:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:9-Luke2:10\">LUK 2:9–2:10</a></p>\n<h3>Fear of the unknown or the abnormal</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:26-Matt14:27\">MAT 14:26–14:27</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:50\">MRK 6:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:19-John6:20\">JHN 6:19–6:20</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:5\">ACT 5:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:18\">EXO 20:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:30\">EXO 34:30</a> <em>The radiance of Moses' face reflected God's glory and made the Israelites afraid</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:5\">DEU 5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam4:7\">1SA 4:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh6:16\">NEH 6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:2\">JER 10:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:9\">DAN 5:9</a> <em>Belshazzar's fear at the writing on the wall</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah1:10\">JON 1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:6\">MAT 17:6</a> <em>the fear of the disciples at the transfiguration</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:54\">MAT 27:54</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:33\">MRK 5:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:32\">MRK 9:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:8\">MRK 16:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:10\">LUK 5:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:37\">LUK 8:37</a> <em>Fear seized the people when the Gerasene demoniac was healed</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:34\">LUK 9:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:8\">JHN 19:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:17\">ACT 19:17</a></p>\n<h2>Fear of embarrassment or shame</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:10\">GEN 3:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:4\">ISA 54:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:20\">JHN 3:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:20\">2CO 12:20</a></p>\n<h2>Fear of the future</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:46\">JER 51:46</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:23\">ISA 41:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:32\">MRK 10:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:32\">LUK 12:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:24\">ACT 27:24</a></p>\n<h2>Fear of persecution</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra4:4\">EZR 4:4</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:42-John12:43\">JHN 12:42–12:43</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:3\">1KI 19:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:13\">JHN 7:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:22\">JHN 9:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:19\">JHN 20:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:14\">1PE 3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:10\">REV 2:10</a></p>\n<h2>Fear of death</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:14-Heb2:15\">HEB 2:14–2:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps55:4-Ps55:5\">PSA 55:4–55:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:36\">MRK 5:36</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:50\">LUK 8:50</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:10\">ACT 23:10</a></p>\n<h2>Fear of people</h2>\n<h3>Of enemies</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:10\">EXO 14:10</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam7:7\">1SA 7:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num22:3\">NUM 22:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg7:3\">JDG 7:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:24\">1SA 17:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:11\">1SA 17:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam10:19\">2SA 10:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr12:5\">2CH 12:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:1-Ps27:3\">PSA 27:1–27:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps56:1-Ps56:4\">PSA 56:1–56:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa20:5\">ISA 20:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:5\">ISA 41:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:25\">JER 22:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer41:18\">JER 41:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Obad1:9\">OBA 1:9</a></p>\n<h3>Of one's own family</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen32:11\">GEN 32:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen45:3\">GEN 45:3</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:21\">JDG 9:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:31\">GEN 31:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen32:7\">GEN 32:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen42:4\">GEN 42:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen50:19\">GEN 50:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:27\">JDG 6:27</a></p>\n<h3>Of particular people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:24\">1SA 15:24</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:3\">1CO 2:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:7\">GEN 26:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod2:14\">EXO 2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut2:4\">DEU 2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:15\">1SA 18:15</a> <em>Saul's fear of David</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam3:11\">2SA 3:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:2\">NEH 2:2</a> <em>Nehemiah's fear before the king</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth7:6\">EST 7:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer26:21\">JER 26:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:19\">JER 38:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:22\">MAT 2:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:12\">MRK 12:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:21\">LUK 19:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:26\">ACT 9:26</a> <em>the disciples fear of Paul, not believing his conversion</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:10\">1CO 16:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:15\">2CO 7:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:12\">GAL 2:12</a></p>\n<h3>Of human beings in general</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:25\">PRO 29:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:17\">DEU 1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:7\">ISA 51:7</a></p>\n<h2>Fear of judgment</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek11:8\">EZK 11:8</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts24:25\">ACT 24:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam28:20\">1SA 28:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr21:30\">1CH 21:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:14\">ISA 33:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:18\">JER 17:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer30:5\">JER 30:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer42:15-Jer42:16\">JER 42:15–42:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek12:18\">EZK 12:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:35\">EZK 27:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:5\">ZEC 9:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:18\">1JN 4:18</a> <em>Christians, assured of God's love, no longer fear judgment</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:10\">REV 18:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:15\">REV 18:15</a></p>\n<h2>Fear as a deterrent</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:4\">ROM 13:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut13:11\">DEU 13:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut17:13\">DEU 17:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut19:20\">DEU 19:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut21:21\">DEU 21:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:28-Job19:29\">JOB 19:28–19:29</a></p>\n<h2>Fear as an opportunity for faith</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:21\">DEU 1:21</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps23:4\">PSA 23:4</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:25-Prov3:26\">PRO 3:25–3:26</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:29-Matt10:31\">MAT 10:29–10:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:13\">EXO 14:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:29\">DEU 1:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:18-Deut7:21\">DEU 7:18–7:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:6\">DEU 31:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh11:6\">JOS 11:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:14\">NEH 4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps3:6\">PSA 3:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:4\">PSA 34:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:5\">PSA 49:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps56:3\">PSA 56:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:24\">ISA 10:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa35:3-Isa35:4\">ISA 35:3–35:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:14\">ISA 41:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:5\">ISA 43:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:8\">ISA 44:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:12\">ISA 51:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:8\">JER 1:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:17\">JER 1:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer30:10\">JER 30:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer42:11\">JER 42:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer46:27\">JER 46:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek2:6\">EZK 2:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:9\">EZK 3:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:19\">DAN 10:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:26\">MAT 8:26</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:40\">MRK 4:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:25\">LUK 8:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:49-Mark6:51\">MRK 6:49–6:51</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:27\">JHN 14:27</a></p>",
